{"tid":843490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駐外使館慶祝「刀割」五星紅旗 網民：撕裂中國！","createTime":"2018-10-01T07:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T09:43:52.000Z","uid":54337,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"60754d96c23ceacf14c58323ff6cc8548d1a5194","tid":843490,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"【十．一假期】駐外使館慶祝「刀割」五星紅旗 網民：撕裂中國！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20181001/58743569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743569&d=nlBVOU48iSINXS0LVaR%2FYy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=265a36e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F58743569&h=30746e5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20181001/58743569</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181001/large/1538371609_d7bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F1538371609_d7bf.jpg&h=eced2edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在香港一旦發現五星紅旗被人破壞，警方必定調查，不過，在中共慶祝建政69周年時，網民上載保加利亞使館舉行招待會的照片，照片中顯示一名女子手持利刀，切開一個有五星紅旗圖案的蛋糕，照片引發內地網民極大反感，批評涉事者是「手切國旗，撕裂中國」，更揚言發現事件屬實，可能就會違反國旗法，「就該被雙規了」。<br />\n<br />\n照片中央顯示一個有五星紅旗圖案的長方型蛋糕，一名女子拿着利刀，在紅旗中一刀切下，旁邊的男子的高的拍手。上載的網民稱，在招待會上有外交官致詞，之後便切五星紅旗蛋糕，然後分給與會者享用。<br />\n<br />\n照片在內地社交媒體上廣傳，網民質疑：「對於外交使節的智商和常識都感到困惑！」「臥槽​​​，這確實不妥啊！」「讓我想起來八國聯軍切大清的蛋糕地圖，太形象了！」「違反國旗法，判刑！」<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"1ff3ab53cc7e671fb00f7f49ee24552944e7f8cc","tid":843490,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T07:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6a49e4b41cad701086d6c6da3898da5cffefb8","tid":843490,"uid":511,"like":1,"d